  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the effect of individual user involvement in an
      outpatient mental health center. The intervention consists of patients completing a
      self-report symptom and problem questionnaire and reviewing it with a clinician.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
